Attribution

dockyard_rl was developed with reference to NVIDIA NeMo-RL, a distributed
reinforcement-learning post-training library by NVIDIA Corporation, licensed
under the Apache License, Version 2.0.

NeMo-RL was used as a design and implementation reference during the
development, upgrading, and ongoing evolution of dockyard_rl — including the
distributed-RL architecture, the GRPO / clipped-policy-gradient formulation,
and the Ray-based fleet orchestration. dockyard_rl is an independent,
standalone re-implementation rather than a fork; its lineage traces to NeMo-RL.

I gratefully acknowledge the NeMo-RL authors and NVIDIA Corporation.

